<div class="special-report-header">
  <h4>
    Special report:
    <a href="/specialreports?year[value][year]=2012&amp;category=76984">Manufacturing and innovation</a>  </h4>
      <div class="special-report-article-list">
      <strong>In this special report</strong>
      <ul class="special-report-article-links"><li class="0 first"><a href="/node/21552901">A third industrial revolution</a></li>
